    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by and see it for yourself!",
