    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution, with bushings and dampers providing a communicative, analog driving experience. While the paintwork reflects its status as a driven machine, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive. This is a performance-first specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes engineering excellence and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear only. Runs well.",
