    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, showing only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light use. Inside, you'll find a pristine, non-smoker cabin with premium upholstery that remains firm and comfortable; all electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. With deep tire treads and responsive braking, it provides a smooth, confident driving experience. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, complete with all original manuals and a clean service record.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
